t: "Ask ňĻthem, O Prophetňļ, ‚ÄúWho provides for you from heaven and earth? Who owns ňĻyourňļ hearing and sight? Who brings forth the living from the dead and the dead from the living? And who conducts every affair?‚ÄĚ They will ňĻsurelyňļ say, ‚ÄúGod.‚ÄĚ Say, ‚ÄúWill you not then fear ňĻHimňļ"